Inspect and update fotingo configuration values.

Examples:
  # Browse config values interactively
  fotingo config view

  # Get a specific key
  fotingo config get git.remote

  # Update a key
  fotingo config set git.remote upstream

Usage:
  fotingo config [command]

Available Commands:
  get         Get one configuration value or browse all keys
  set         Set a configuration value
  view        Interactively browse configuration keys

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for config

Global Flags:
  -b, --branch string   Base branch override (default: auto-detect)
      --debug           Show diagnostic output (includes verbose)
      --json            Output results as JSON
      --no-color        Disable colored output
      --quiet           Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose         Show step-level progress output
  -y, --yes             Accept defaults without prompting

Use "fotingo config [command] --help" for more information about a command.
